&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Accounting Manager&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Department: &lt;/strong&gt;Finance&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reports To: &lt;/strong&gt;CFO&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location: &lt;/strong&gt;Tampa, FL&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Naked Farmer is entering a period of rapid expansion, and we are building the financial infrastructure needed to support that growth.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We are seeking an Assistant Controller to help strengthen the accounting foundation of the company — improving close processes, building internal controls, and supporting the systems required for a growing multi-unit restaurant platform.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;This role will work closely with the Controller and CFO to ensure financial accuracy across a growing portfolio of restaurants while helping prepare the organization for its first financial statement review and future audit.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;For someone who enjoys building systems, improving processes, and operating in a high-growth environment, this role offers the opportunity to play a meaningful role in shaping the accounting function of a scaling company. This role provides a clear pathway toward a future Controller position as the company continues to grow.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Build&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;A disciplined monthly close process&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Strong internal controls and accounting documentation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Scalable systems and workflows inside Restaurant365&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Clean integrations between POS, delivery platforms, payroll, and accounting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Audit-ready financial reporting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Monthly Close &amp;amp; Financial Reporting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Help lead the monthly, quarterly, and annual close processes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;• Ensure accurate financial reporting across multiple restaurant locations&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;• Review journal entries, reconciliations, and financial statements&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;• Maintain balance sheet integrity through reconciliations and variance analysis&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;• Improve close timelines and standardize accounting procedures&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Restaurant Revenue &amp;amp; Operational Accounting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12p

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;The Catering Sales Manager reports directly to the Chief Operating Officer and is responsible for working in partnership with Restaurant Catering Leads to drive market catering sales from Fort Lauderdale to Miami and everywhere in between. The CSM is responsible for sourcing leads, developing, and maintaining client relationships, and securing catering sales for the South Florida Market.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reports to the Chief Operating Officer to define market sales strategy and develop tactical plans to achieve quarterly sales targets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drives Catering Sales business performance by daily prospecting via phone, canvassing, and conducting on-site client tastings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and grow relationships with key accounts to maximize sales potential and frequency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Works closely with Catering Leads and Chef Operators to support sales strategies and effectively execute tactics that grow Catering sales locally.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contact lapsed customers to understand how their catering needs have changed and build relationships to drive future catering sales.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide regular sales updates to your operations team to foster a competitive environment and reward excellence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in local events, activations and various networking opportunities to ensure highest ROI.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in Business Administration, Hospitality Management, or other relevant major preferred. Equivalent relevant work experience may be accepted in lieu of degree.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3-5 years sales experience required; business-to-business sales with a consultative selling approach preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track record of consistently reaching or exceeding sales goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sales experience in a catering and/or restaurant environment strongly desired.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong cold calling and sales presentation skills, and ability to turn leads into sales.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Professional presence, ability to adapt message and approach to the audience, and ability to relate to a wide variety of people and tailor communication accordingly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong written and verbal communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-starter with the ability to work autonomously.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to overcome objections and handle challenges with a consistent and professional presence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experienced selling to a wide cross section of channels (i.e. corporate, medical, athletics, education, retail, etc.) with a focus on B2B sales.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong knowledge of local/regional corporate sales opportunities and experience at successfully targeting key decision makers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficient with using and maximizing Salesforce Customer Relationship Management (CRM) software.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficient in Spanish language preferred but not required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We Offer:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A competitive base salary, plus bonus and commissions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Paid time off&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Near-future benefits package that includes: health, dental, vision, and telemedicine&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free Naked Farmer food&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The opportunity to be on the ground floor of a rapidly growing brand&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Physical Requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to maintain a stationary position to be able to operate a computer and other office equipment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be able to identify, analyze and assess details&lt;/li&gt;
